title: Fun Fact #1
body: My first Pokémon game was Ultra Moon, I got it in 2018. I did this because since I started doing many new things in 2018, I called 2018 the “year of new things”. And since I always wondered what playing a Pokémon game would be like, I thought “what the hell” and bought it.

summary:
Caretaker Notes:
Lots of playtime
Lots of socialization
Pay attention to possible joint pain and report it
Strict diet - only...
body:
Zippy

Caretaker Notes:

  • Lots of playtime
  • Lots of socialization
  • Pay attention to possible joint pain and report it
  • Strict diet - only berry treats
  • She’s a cuddler - careful of static buildup

Zippy was rescued from a neglect case where she was confined and given improper diet. While Pikachus are popular for good reason, they’re loyal, intelligent and loving creatures not everyone is suitable to care for their needs, including lots of stimuli and exercise to keep their body and mind healthy.

Through strict diet, exercise and lots of playtime, Zippy will soon be able to be as active as she likes without the stress on her joints.
